Decorative markers (emph, strong) are dropped — plain reading is unchanged.
```
Hello _world_, welcome.
.
Hello world, welcome.
```

Strong is dropped.
```
Please *stop* that.
.
Please stop that.
```

Mark is dropped.
```
It was {=highlighted=} text.
.
It was highlighted text.
```

Insert is dropped (the text is still present, so no meaning is lost).
```
A list: one, two, {+three+}.
.
A list: one, two, three.
```
